NAME
    pager -- text pager

SYNOPSIS
    pager [file]

DESCRIPTION
    pager displays a file and allows it to be navigated in full-screen. If no
    file is specified, it will read stdin until EOF is encountered, and then it
    will display the accumulated buffer. It is used by (0)help to display topic
    pages.
